&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>서명 생성 단계: 서명자의 개인키로 해시값을 암호화하여 서명을 생성한다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code">
&lt;div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">def&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nf">detailed_signing_process&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">private_key&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">document&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">):&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;서명 과정의 세부 단계 표시&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="c1"># 1. 문서 해시 생성&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">document_hash&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">create_document_hash&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">document&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="c1"># 2. 해시값을 개인키로 암호화하여 서명 생성&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">signature&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">private_key&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">sign&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">document_hash&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">padding&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">PSS&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">mgf&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">padding&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">MGF1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">hashes&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">SHA256&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()),&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">salt_length&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">padding&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">PSS&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">MAX_LENGTH&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">),&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">hashes&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">SHA256&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">signature&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">document_hash&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0">
